Third-party data attributions

Lebedev quadrature tables (src/quadrature_lebedev_data.c) are derived from the
public work of V.I. Lebedev and D.N. Laikov, "A quadrature formula for the
sphere of the 131st algebraic order of accuracy," Doklady Mathematics 59 (3),
477-481 (1999). The specific node and weight values are public domain.

Reference Clebsch-Gordan and 3j/6j/9j values under tests/reference_data/ were
generated by a committed sympy script (tests/reference_data/generate_references.py)
at repository setup time. Sympy is distributed under the BSD-3-Clause license;
no sympy code is redistributed in this library.
